# Cursor Rules

## Code Style
- Follow biome.json rules
- 2 spaces, 100 line width, double quotes
- TypeScript: avoid `any`, use `const`, template literals
- Remove unused imports/variables

## Project Structure
- `admin/`: React + Vite frontend
- `elysia-server/`: Elysia.js backend

## Before Committing
Run: `bun biome check --write .`
